      • loadDocumentQuiet

        public Document loadDocumentQuiet(GraphRewrite event,
                                  org.ocpsoft.rewrite.context.EvaluationContext context,
                                  XmlFileModel model)
        Loads and parses the provided XML file. This will quietly fail (not throwing an Exception) and return null if it is unable to parse the provided XmlFileModel. A ClassificationModel will be created to indicate that this file failed to parse.
        Returns:
        Returns either the parsed Document or null if the Document could not be parsed
